{"tid":480310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批拉布勞民傷財　張宇人籲公眾支持修改議事規則：這是你們的錢！","createTime":"2017-11-26T04:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T13:41:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfeff63d4819e7908f4977e978f4620ed7a3c9a","tid":480310,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171126/s00001/9beb2878039e4b349f0383be38cff9e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171126%2Fs00001%2F9beb2878039e4b349f0383be38cff9e1.jpg&h=238bc612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會修改《議事規則》拉鋸戰持續，行政會議成員、立法會自由黨議員張宇人出席港台英文節目「給香港的信」表示，泛民議員指摘建制修改《議事規則》等同「自我閹割」的說法，僅是「吸引公眾注意的口號」。他又批評泛民「拉布」做法勞民傷財，並寄語市民「這是你們的金錢被不必要地扔入溝渠裏」。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人指，泛民議員經常製造輿論，稱建制舉動是剝削他們的言論自由及監察政府權力，又批評這等同立法會的「自我閹割」，但他稱，泛民這些「冠冕堂皇」的言論，僅僅是「吸引公眾注意的口號」。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，近年泛民在大會以及各小組委員會進行「拉布」阻礙會議，不但癱瘓立法會，更令會議時間被不必要地延長，導致立法、公共財政撥款、基建項目開發等過程受阻，嚴重妨害香港經濟發展及民生改善。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人又表示，「拉布」並不能阻止議案通過，僅是延長審議時間。<br />\n<br />\n他以14/15年度擔任財委會主席時的經歷為例，指他就任頭三個月處理的，是上一立法年度積留的議案，雖然積留議案在6個月後陸續獲得通過，但因通脹緣故，有關議案需要額外28億元撥款。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人向市民表示，「這是你們的金錢，被不必要地扔入溝渠裏（This is your money, thrown down the drain unnecessarily）」，稱修改《議事規則》可維護立法會尊嚴，呼籲公眾支持，讓立法會重返正軌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171126/s00001/1511660763604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171126%2Fs00001%2F1511660763604&d=pdfsOOv%2BpbPhoedP6gJH9xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=cf9c5be9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171126%2Fs00001%2F1511660763604&h=2d05819a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171126/s00001/1511660763604</a>"},{"pid":"5c063de8600d2d72f364d36f06fa431cdf1158fb","tid":480310,"uid":531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得三跑高鐵港珠澳勞民傷財浪費納稅人金錢，可唔可以回水？"},{"pid":"288fa8860ebcac689e24b6379cbd239303578143","tid":480310,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:56:13.000Z","msg":"Yes, this is our money<br />\n<br />\n所以我地唔想出糧比你地班政府高官，乞食啦你"},{"pid":"0fdf500e01e67829cd9866a8941f67c142099478","tid":480310,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"你份糧係香港人 d 錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578a7922641e1547504eaaaeb376411563940a1f","tid":480310,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"唔通唔拉布 啲錢會用番落香港人身上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1f3da2b6d423ed36e927513955f074b0a0cec4","tid":480310,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"咁直接廢除立法會算啦，政府話乜就乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12e8c2dd959f1c530a3da43cf157438e133fcd6","tid":480310,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476ddabb344259a993a8cb61074b35290ad80db1","tid":480310,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"筆錢從來都唔係我哋，更加唔係佢，筆錢係香港政治自願畀留畀中共洗，就算洗哂香港政府都唔怕，到時直接用人仔代港元，但係中國就會用港元兌換而來嘅美元入自已袋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743aad5b9b58c4df8e343eb5894e35f568bdf8e0","tid":480310,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}